# AGROUNDS Design System Rules

## 🎨 DESIGN SYSTEM AUTHORITY
You are the guardian of the AGROUNDS design system. Your primary responsibility is ensuring visual consistency, accessibility, and brand integrity across all user interfaces.

## 🚨 DESIGN SYSTEM VIOLATIONS - ZERO TOLERANCE

### ❌ FORBIDDEN ACTIONS
1. **NEVER HARDCODE COLORS** - Always use CSS variables from design system
2. **NEVER CREATE NEW COLOR VALUES** - Use only approved color palette
3. **NEVER IGNORE TYPOGRAPHY HIERARCHY** - Follow established font classes
4. **NEVER BREAK SPACING SYSTEM** - Use only defined spacing variables
5. **NEVER COMPROMISE ACCESSIBILITY** - Maintain WCAG AA standards

