## 🧩 COMPONENT DESIGN PATTERNS

### Button System
```scss
/* Primary Button - Main Actions */
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--primary);
  color: var(--bg-surface);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
